### 8. Get current user — valid token
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 9. Get current user — no token (should return 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me

###

### 10. Get current user — fake token (should return 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer thisisafaketoken


### ───────────────────────────────
### REFRESH + LOGOUT
### ───────────────────────────────

### 11. Refresh token
### (refresh_token cookie is set automatically by REST Client from login response)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh

###

### 12. Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 13. Refresh after logout (should return 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh


### ───────────────────────────────
### VERIFICATION
### ───────────────────────────────

### 14. Submit address — valid
POST {{baseUrl}}/verification/submit-address
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "Connaught Place, New Delhi, India"
}

###

### 15. Submit address — no token (should return 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/verification/submit-address
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "Connaught Place, New Delhi, India"
}

###

### 16. Submit address — bad address (should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/verification/submit-address
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "xyzzy fake street 999999"
}

###

### 17. Request postcard
POST {{baseUrl}}/verification/request-postcard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 18. Request postcard again — already verified check
### (run this after confirming postcard, should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/verification/request-postcard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ───────────────────────────────
### CONFIRM POSTCARD
### paste the 6-digit code from request-postcard response below
### ───────────────────────────────

@postcardCode = 395896

### 19. Confirm postcard — valid code
POST {{baseUrl}}/verification/confirm-postcard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "{{postcardCode}}"
}

###

### 20. Confirm postcard — same code again (should return 400, key deleted)
POST {{baseUrl}}/verification/confirm-postcard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "{{postcardCode}}"
}

###

### 21. Confirm postcard — wrong code (should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/verification/confirm-postcard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "000000"
}


### ───────────────────────────────
### USER PROFILE
### paste a real userId from register response below
### ───────────────────────────────

@userId = a9bc305b-f434-4ef5-bd97-b1e613b5a0b3

### 22. Get public profile — valid user
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/profile

###

### 23. Get public profile — fake ID (should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/profile


### ───────────────────────────────
### UPDATE PROFILE
### ───────────────────────────────

### 24. Update display name
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "displayName": "Updated Name"
}

###

### 25. Update notification prefs
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notificationPrefs": {
    "pushAlerts": false
  }
}

###

### 26. Empty body (should return 400)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### 27. No token (should return 401)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "displayName": "Hacker"
}